# Faz 8: Admin Panel

## Goal

Admin panel — system settings (password policy, session timeout, SLA defaults), audit log viewer (search + filter + export + chain verify), consent version management (draft → publish workflow), data retention policy editor, admin dashboard (metrics).

## Bu fazın çalışma modeli (iterasyonlar)

`@58-phase-08-admin-panel` + **“Faz 8 — İterasyon N”**.

### İterasyon 1 — system-settings + audit API

**Hedef:** `system-settings/*`, `audit/*` (list, export rate limit, verify-chain endpoint); Redis cache (5 dk) ayarı; DTO validation.

**Minimum bağlam:** `docs/03_API_CONTRACTS.md` 9.9; `docs/07_SECURITY_IMPLEMENTATION.md` Bölüm 12 özet.

**Bu iterasyonda yok:** consent modülü UI; nightly cron (İter 3).

**Stop:** [ ] Audit API integration testleri (filtre/pagination). PR/onay.

### İterasyon 2 — Consent backend + tüm admin UI sayfaları

**Hedef:** `consent/*` publish workflow; audit log + consent + system settings ekranları; chain verify butonu UX.

**Bu iterasyonda yok:** data-retention cleanup cron (İter 3).

**Stop:** [ ] Consent publish → re-accept akışı testle doğrulandı. PR/onay.

### İterasyon 3 — Worker crons + admin dashboard metrikleri

**Hedef:** `audit-chain-verify-cron`, `data-retention-cleanup-cron`, admin dashboard aggregated queries; permission enforcement testleri.

**Stop:** Faz 8 Done Definition; roadmap işareti.

